BEGIN_TEXT
Let \(f(x)=$a1 \sin(x) \). $BR$BR

$BBOLD a.) $EBOLD \( |f'(x)| \le \) \{ans_rule(10) \}$BR

$BBOLD b.) $EBOLD By the Mean Value Theorem, \(|f(a)-f(b)|\le\) 
\{ans_rule(5) \} \( |a-b| \) for all \(a\) and \(b\).

END_TEXT

ANS(Real($a1)->cmp);
ANS(Real($a1)->cmp);

